item.title: Rap Im Keller #2
item.description: At Kulturhofkeller, we’re establishing a new series of events: Rap in the basement. It is about rap, it is about music, yet it is about so much more: It is about bringing people together and promoting improvisational artforms. Simply put, it is about slick flows and dope freestyles. Hosted by „doppelt sichtbar“ und „Freakygreenfish“.
